CSEM v2.4

- Replaced the Fenwick tree like structure with a linear structure to speed up CSEM
- Added user-friendly reminders if CSEM guesses that users forget to compile the codes
- Added '--no-extending-reads' option to 'run-csem' to disable extending reads
- Added '--tag-align' option to 'csem-generate-input' to support tagAlign format files as inputs for downstream ChIP-Seq peak callers

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CSEM v1.0

- Extend reads to the average fragment length and use the midpoint instead of the left most genomic coordinatefor allocating multi-reads
- Take SAM/BAM formatted files as input and generate BAM formatted outputs
- Generate input files for downstream peak callers using CSEM's BAM formatted file
- Generate wiggle plots for visualization
- Provide a script to extract reads from eland files

